        public Credentials getAnyCredentials()

        • PasswordCredentials
        • SSOCredentials
        • Any other credential type

      • getSSOCredentials

        public SSOCredentials getSSOCredentials(SSOType type,
                               String otherType)
        Get sso credentials for the principal. This will return the first found credential with the given sso type. If the sso type is SSOType.other, then this will also compare the otherType field.
        Parameters:
        type - the sso type
        otherType - optional field, only used when type is SSOType.other
        Returns:
        the credentials or null

      • setCredentials

        public void setCredentials(List<Credentials> creds)
        Set the credentials of the principal. Do not use this. Use getCredentials().clear(), getCredentials().add(..), etc. instead.
        Parameters:
        creds - the principal's credentials.

      • setStatus

        public void setStatus(PrincipalStatus status)
        Set the current status of the principal. This should not be set directly. Instead, use PrincipalDAO.setPrincipalStatus(net.proteusframework.users.model.Principal, net.proteusframework.users.model.PrincipalStatus) to insure consistency between the status and the enabled property.
        Parameters:
        status - the status
